According to The Daily Mail he had a 13-year-relationship with Texan art dealer Kenny Gross who was encouraging the star to get back into music.Michael and Kenny s relationship was made public in 1998 when Michael came out of the closet after his arrest for engaging in a lewd act following a sting in a public toilet by Beverly Hills cops. Kenny continued to support his ex accompanying him to court appearances.After his break-up with Kenny Michael was in a relationship with Fadi Fawas a London-based hair stylist. They were last seen together in September last year.TMG Digital/TimesLIVE